products.title: MISTERHULT Pendant lamp
products.subTitle: Pendant lamp, bamboo/handmade, 45cm
products.description: The idea with MISTERHULT was to make a lamp with a minimal environmental footprint. By letting bamboo, that otherwise would be discarded, enhance the lamp’s expression, we harness the plant more than twice as much.
